data.description: Gorgeous one story home that provides a comfortable aura for its new owners!! With warm paint colors throughout the entirety of the home and a comfortable family room, it's hard not to fall in love!  Laminate flooring throughout,  the 4th bedroom as a study with elegant French doors, and the master bedroom has a luxurious master bath and double vanities that tie it all together.  Don't forget the garden and lush backyard, come be the first to see it !!
